parameters.name: TemplateConfig
parameters.description: The detailed configurations of the AI template. The value is a JSON string. For more information, see [AITemplateConfig](~~89863#title-vd3-499-o36~~).

parameters.name: TemplateId
parameters.description:
The ID of the AI template. You can use one of the following methods to obtain the ID:

*   Call the [AddAITemplate](~~102930~~) operation to add an AI template if no AI template exists. The value of TemplateId in the response is the ID of the AI template.
*   Call the [ListAITemplate](~~102936~~) operation if the template already exists. The value of TemplateId in the response is the ID of the AI template.

parameters.name: TemplateName
parameters.description: The name of the AI template. The name can be up to 128 bytes in length.
